            </div>
            <div class="new-list">
                <div class="new-title">
                    <span >热点聚焦</span>
                    <span>活动公告</span>
                    <span>基层直击</span>
                    <span>文化视窗</span>
                </div>
                <div class="new-inform">
                    <ul>
                        <li><span>2020-06-16</span>重要通知！2021年青海省文化馆老年大学招生考试通知</li>
                        <li><span>2020-06-16</span>中华人民共和国反间谍法</li>
